apped or dropped in downstream annotation maintenance.\n+\n+Validation:\n+\n+- Pre-change validation: `make travis_build` passed.\n+- Post-change validation: `make travis_build` passed.\n+\n+Research and pattern notes:\n+\n+- Created local `RESEARCH.md` and `DESIGN_PATTERNS.md` notes to record annotation-impact analysis and the obsolete-term formatting pattern.\n+- PubMed pages for PMID validation were checked directly in this environment because `linkml-reference-validator cache reference` hit PubMed rate limiting (`HTTP 429`).\n+\n+Checklist:\n+\n+- [x] PLAN: analyzed issue context and obsoletion request\n+- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: ontology validated before edits\n+- [x] RESEARCH: annotation/publication impact reviewed and documented locally\n+- [x] TERM-SEARCH: checked `GO:0009095`, `GO:0009094`, and `GO:0006571`\n+- [x] DESIGN-PATTERNS: applied obsolete-term pattern guidance\n+- [x] EDITS: used `obo-checkout.pl` and `obo-checkin.pl`\n+- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: removed obsolete logical axioms and retained only obsoletion metadata\n+- [x] SPECIALIZED-EDITS: used obsoletion workflow\n+- [x] METADATA: preserved historical definition provenance and added correct issue tracker item\n+- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: `make travis_build` passed after edits\n+- [x] REFERENCE-VALIDATION: PMIDs checked directly via PubMed fetches; rate-limit issue noted\n+- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: ontology change committed locally\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,51 @@\n+Obsoleted `GO:0009095` aromatic amino acid biosynthetic process, prephenate pathway.\n+\n+Rationale:\n+\n+- The term mapped to `MetaCyc:PWY-3481`, which is a superpathway combining the L-phenylalanine and L